     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       Mny f th prblms w’r xprncng s  scty cm frm mnfctrd dsr. Obsty, dbt, fnncl crss, n vrbndnc f stff, cnsmrsm, glbl wrmng, nd s n … thy hppn bcs w r nvr cntnt, lwys wntng mr, nd cn’t cntrl r dsrs. Ths dsrs hv bn mnfctrd by dvrtsng nd chmcls (frnch frs hvng chmcls tht mk s wnt thm, tc.).
      </p>
      <p>
       Advrtsrs hv stdd th mchnsms f hmn dsr, nd hv prfctd th crft f mkng s wnt thngs. Chldrn wtchng  crtn, fr xmpl, wll t mr sncks f thr r ds fr fd drng th crtn (t dsn’t mttr wht knd f fd), s ppsd t ds fr thr prdcts. Ppl wh s th Pd cn’t cntrl thr dsr t by n, bcs thy’r s cl! Crs, hss, clths, gdgts, fd, trvl, y nm t, w hv bn trnd t wnt thm by dvrtsng.
      </p>
      <p>
       Hw ds  hmn bng, r  scty fr tht mttr, fght sch dsrs? It’s prtty dmn hrd. Try wlkng thrgh n Appl str, r wlkng by th fd crt wth ts smlls f frsh pzzs r cnnmn bns, r wtchng tlvsn, wtht dsrng. Sm ppl cn cntrl thmslvs, r hv trnd thmslvs t ssct ths thngs wth ngtv thghts (fttnng, grsy, plstc, sprfcl, tc.), bt mst f s rn’t tht dscplnd.
      </p>
      <p>
       Th nswr s tht, jst s th dsrs hv bn mnfctrd crflly nd wth mch ffrt, w mst mnfctr cntnt. In rslvs, nd n scty.
      </p>
      <p>
       Hw wld w d tht? I’d strt by rmvng yrslf frm plcs whr dvrtsng s s prvsv:
       <span class="caps">
        TV,
       </span>
       mgzns, mlls. Fnd d-fr cntnt, r t lst mnml dvrtsng: pblc rd, r d-lss blgs, tc. Fnd wys t spnd yr tm wtht hvng t g t th mll. Avd shppng wbsts. Bt vn bynd tht, I thnk w cn rch thrs t shw thm hw t b cntnt.
      </p>
      <p>
       Mnfctrng cntnt mns dvlpng  strng, cnsstnt mssg … smthng lng th lns f “Y lrdy hv ngh”. Or bttr — I cn’t sy I hv th nswrs hr. W wld wnt t rch ppl wh r bt t gv n t thr dsrs, prhps n tlvsn r n th mlls r n th Intrnt. W’d nd  cmpgn tht wld drv ths mssg hm, nd dct ppl bt th dngrs f mnfctrd dsr, nd shw ppl hw t fnd cntntdnss.
      </p>
      <p>
       Imgn  bg wht bllbrd n Tms Sqr wth th smpl mssg: “Y lrdy hv ngh.”
      </p>
      <p>
       Imgn tht w bght ds n Amzn, tht pprd bfr ppl bght smthng: “Y dn’t nd tht, my frnd.” OK, s Amzn wld nvr llw n d lk tht n thr st, bt y gt th d.
      </p>
      <p>
       Imgn tht crdt crds cm wth th mssg “Y dn’t wnt dbt” prntd n thm.
      </p>
      <p>
       Imgn n Phn prtng systm tht dtctd whn y’r bt t g shppng n  wbst, nd tld y, “B cntnt wth wht y hv. Lt g f dsr.”
      </p>
      <p>
       Imgn f McDnld’s drv-thrs wr lnd wth bllbrds tht rd, “Dn’t b  glttn. Et lss, t sstnbly. Dn’t sprsz, smplfy.”
      </p>
      <p>
       Imgn f chldrn wr tght nt tht thy nd t g by th ltst Dsny tys, r vd gm systm, bt t njy ntr, t lv lf smply nd flly.
      </p>
      <p>
       Cntntdnss cms ntrlly, n th bsnc f mnfctrd dsr. Bt gttng bck t tht ntrl stt mght tk sm wrk.
